content: Excellent, easy to use, analysis of readings informative. Particularly useful as I suffer quite badly from white coat syndrome, therefore useful info when discussing with the doctor.
Not bad at all. Recommended.
False info do not use

Got a normal reading - my wife who is a nurse took my blood pressure and it 
is dangerously high - DO NOT TRUST OR USE THIS APP
My Dr recommended it to me. Very easy to chart.

I used the app to take 100 readings over six weeks after my family doctor asked me to monitor my blood pressure for a while. The app is easy to use, records everything that needs recording, and the export-to-PDF functionality allowed me to generate a report that was, literally, exactly what the doctor ordered. Kudos.
Material Design support is needed.
Waste of money
Easy to use. One of my essential medical apps.
This app requires you to make an initial purchase to download the app and then another second purchase to export your data. That's just stupid, don't try to hide the real price of the app.
Tried to export but wouldn't unlock
Excellent app
It is clean and efficient. Works great.
Great app for tracking bp

Time is offset. Taking your blood pressure in the afternoon and it will be registered as being taken in the morning. Take your  blood pressure in the morning and it will be registered as taken in the evening.
replyContent: Thank you for your feedback. In the latest version (3.1), we added a settings option to define start and end of the provided time periods: morning, afternoon, evening, and night. Does this solve your problem? If not, please let us know: http://medando.de/kontakt/feedback/?lang=en and we will follow up with you.

content: Excellent product but seems to be missing one function for me I need to be able to either print or send 4/6weekly report to doctor problem is they need a complete 4 week daily am/pm list with all the figures and not just average figures, if this option is available then will change my rating to 5 stars and would be willing to pay for it
I recently switched to Android & needed to replace the iPhone app I was using. This one turned out to be a good replacement.
